      • roundedimageview_border_inside_color

        public static final int roundedimageview_border_inside_color

        This symbol is the offset where the R.attr.border_inside_color attribute's value can be found in the roundedimageview array.

        Must be a color value, in the form of "#rgb", "#argb", "#rrggbb", or "#aarrggbb".

        This may also be a reference to a resource (in the form "@[package:]type:name") or theme attribute (in the form "?[package:][type:]name") containing a value of this type.

      • roundedimageview_border_thickness

        public static final int roundedimageview_border_thickness

        This symbol is the offset where the R.attr.border_thickness attribute's value can be found in the roundedimageview array.

        Must be a dimension value, which is a floating point number appended with a unit such as "14.5sp". Available units are: px (pixels), dp (density-independent pixels), sp (scaled pixels based on preferred font size), in (inches), mm (millimeters).

        This may also be a reference to a resource (in the form "@[package:]type:name") or theme attribute (in the form "?[package:][type:]name") containing a value of this type.
